snippet.title: Zafe's Adventures - SAGE 2024 Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
The demo for my small platformer game is finally here! Exclusively during SAGE 2024 event, check out the game here: https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/zafes-adventures.2199/

The bad news is, that kind of demo that I made recently is just getting really buggy and quirky for sometimes since my programming skill isn't better enough. So anyways, hope you guys enjoy a little demo with oddly shoddy stuff and you can expect this.

Play the previous demo here:
https://gamejolt.com/games/zafeadventures/838455

Thank to you guys for subscribing my YouTube channel, participating at SAGE 2024 event and enjoys my little game here! ^^

Music: All The Way by Liam The Lemming
Obtained from The Mod Archive
https://modarchive.org/index.php?request=view_by_moduleid&query=72337
